le Ages, and thence into England. It was a royal name, and its enduring popularity may have been enhanced by the fact that it was borne by a queen of England—  Isabella  (  1296–1358 ), daughter of  Philip IV  of France—even though she led a turbulent life and eventually had her husband,  Edward II , murdered."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Isabella de Bretton was born in 1346. She married Richard Bernehaud. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died after 1362."},"et":{"1346–after 1362":"1346–pärast 1362","1345–1362":"1345–1362","1365–1439":"1365–1439","1346–1362":"1346–1362","1346":"1346","1345":"1345","1365":"1365","1362":"1362","after 1362":"pärast 1362","Aft 1362":"pärast 1362","1439":"1439","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1346–after 1362":"1346–1362 jälkeen","1345–1362":"1345–1362","1365–1439":"1365–1439","1346–1362":"1346–1362","1346":"1346","1345":"1345","1365":"1365","1362":"1362","after 1362":"1362 jälkeen","Aft 1362":"1362 jälkeen","1439":"1439","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1346–after 1362":"1346–après 1362","1345–1362":"1345–1362","1365–1439":"1365–1439","1346–1362":"1346–1362","1346":"1346","1345":"1345","1365":"1365","1362":"1362","after 1362":"après 1362","Aft 1362":"après 1362","1439":"1439","England, United Kingdom":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Isabella de Bretton est née en 1346. Elle a épousé Richard Bernehaud. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Elle est décédée après 1362."},"de":{"1346–after 1362":"1346–nach 1362","1345–1362":"1345–1362","1365–1439":"1365–1439","1346–1362":"1346–1362","1346":"1346","1345":"1345","1365":"1365","1362":"1362","after 1362":"nach 1362","Aft 1362":"nach 1362","1439":"1439","England, United Kingdom":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Isabella de Bretton wurde 1346 geboren. Sie hat Richard Bernehaud geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Tochter. Sie starb nach 1362."},"ht":{"1346–after 1362":"1346–after 1362","1345–1362":"1345–1362","136